Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: The Bess Myerson trial begins
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00ydrwr
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 28 Oct 1988
The 1988 trial of Bess Myerson, the former Miss America and head of consumer affairs to New York City, accused of tax fraud and bribing a judge.